ispanic and Latino American writers| List]]\n[[Category:Lists of American writers|Puerto]]\n", "name_user": "Lawrlafo", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eP-Q:integrated several authors whose last names begin with P", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Puerto_Rican_writers"}
